body:
My hopes is a centering effect similar to elastic layout.

The below 2 ways both can not do it.

[not in center of cell]
worksheet.addImage(imageId2, {
  tl: { col: 0, row: 0 },
  ext: { width: 500, height: 200 }
});

or 

[Fill all place of Cell]
worksheet.addImage(imageId2, 'B2:D6');


Thank you guys.
